-- Belka Says Zloty Gains on Confidence in Emerging Markets
-- B y   K a t y a   A n d r u s z
-- 2012-03-23T14:07:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-23/belka-says-zloty-gains-on-confidence-in-emerging-markets-1-.html
The zloty’s rally this year was
spurred by growing investors’ confidence in emerging markets,
central bank Governor Marek Belka said in Warsaw today.  The  European Central Bank ’s three-year loans to euro-area
banks have “very much helped” Poland’s economy, Belka said at
a central bank ceremony honoring participants of the high-school
Economics Olympics.  To contact the reporter on this story:
